|`AdaptationOn`|<span data-ttu-id="0abba-461">Указывает, является ли адаптации акустическими модели ON (значение = `1`) или OFF (значение = `0`).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0abba-461">Indicates whether adaptation of the acoustic model is ON (value = `1`) or OFF (value = `0`).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0abba-462">Значение по умолчанию — `1` (ON).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0abba-462">The default value is `1` (ON).</span></span>|  
